@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Nuestra Historia";
}

<div class="relative w-full -mt-24 md:-mt-32 h-[80vh] min-h-[600px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-charcoal-900">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606787366850-de6330128bfc?q=80&w=1920&auto=format&fit=crop"
             alt="Maestro Carnicero"
             class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 fixed-parallax">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#050505] via-black/60 to-black/30"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <span class="block text-gold-500 font-slab font-bold tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-xs md:text-sm mb-6 animate-fade-in-down">
            Desde 1985
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white uppercase leading-[0.9] drop-shadow-2xl mb-8 animate-slide-in-up">
            Más que Embutidos, <br />
            <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-rust-500 to-red-600">Un Legado</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg md:text-2xl font-serif italic font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
            "La calidad no es un acto, es un hábito que hemos perfeccionado durante tres generaciones."
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white/50" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
        </svg>
    </div>
</div>

<section class="py-24 md:py-40 bg-[#050505] relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/wood-pattern.png')] opacity-5 pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">

            <div class="relative group">
                <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-rust-600/20 blur-2xl rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
                <div class="relative z-10 border-[1px] border-white/10 p-4">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551024709-8f23befc6f87?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop"
                         alt="El Origen"
                         class="w-full h-auto object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000 shadow-2xl">

                    <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 bg-gold-500 text-black w-32 h-32 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center p-2 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(234,179,8,0.4)] animate-spin-slow">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="100" height="100">
                            <path id="curve" d="M 50, 50 m -37, 0 a 37,37 0 1,1 74,0 a 37,37 0 1,1 -74,0" fill="transparent" />
                            <text width="500">
                                <textPath xlink:href="#curve" class="font-black text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em]">
                                    • Original • Auténtico • Calidad •
                                </textPath>
                            </text>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="absolute text-2xl font-black">ET</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <span class="text-rust-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-xs mb-4 block border-l-4 border-rust-500 pl-4">El Origen</span>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black font-slab text-white mb-8 leading-tight">
                    La Obsesión de <br /><span class="text-gold-500">"El Tío"</span>
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed font-light">
                    <p>
                        Todo comenzó en una pequeña granja familiar en los valles de Cochabamba. Mientras otros buscaban producir más rápido, nuestro fundador tenía una sola obsesión: <strong>encontrar la carne perfecta</strong>.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        "No se puede apresurar al sabor", solía decir. Esa filosofía rebelde contra la industria masiva es lo que hoy nos define. No utilizamos atajos, ni extensores, ni prisas.
                    </p>
                    <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-white/20 pl-6 py-2 my-8 italic text-white font-serif text-xl">
                        "La comida une a la familia, pero el sabor crea los recuerdos."
                    </blockquote>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="py-32 bg-[#e8e4d9] relative text-charcoal-900">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cream-paper.png')] opacity-60"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black font-slab uppercase text-charcoal-900 mb-4">Nuestros Pilares</h2>
            <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-rust-600 mx-auto"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">

            <div class="group relative p-8 border border-charcoal-900/10 hover:border-rust-600 transition-all duration-500 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-rust-600 transform scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500"></div>

                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-charcoal-900 text-gold-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-xl group-hover:bg-rust-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>

                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase mb-4 tracking-wide">Selección Premium</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Solo trabajamos con proveedores certificados. Ganado criado en libertad y alimentado naturalmente. Sin hormonas, sin secretos.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="group relative p-8 border border-charcoal-900/10 hover:border-rust-600 transition-all duration-500 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-rust-600 transform scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500"></div>

                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-charcoal-900 text-gold-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-xl group-hover:bg-rust-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.384-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>

                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase mb-4 tracking-wide">Ciencia & Arte</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Fusionamos recetas de antaño con tecnología de vanguardia para garantizar la inocuidad sin perder el alma del sabor.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="group relative p-8 border border-charcoal-900/10 hover:border-rust-600 transition-all duration-500 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-rust-600 transform scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500"></div>

                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-charcoal-900 text-gold-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-xl group-hover:bg-rust-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>

                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase mb-4 tracking-wide">Impacto Local</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Apoyamos a 50 familias de ganaderos locales. Comprando El Tío, estás invirtiendo en nuestra comunidad y tierra.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

